/* resources.rc — PE resources embedded into assessment-agent.exe.
 *
 * AGENT_ENV_EXAMPLE: the canonical agent.env.example text. The installer
 * subcommand reads this via FindResourceW(L"AGENT_ENV_EXAMPLE", RT_RCDATA)
 * to seed the on-disk env file and to drive the interactive prompt loop —
 * deploy/agent.env.example stays the single source of truth, but operators
 * never need it on the target host.
 *
 * windres treats RCDATA payload as opaque bytes, so UTF-8 (incl. Korean
 * comments in the example) round-trips intact.
 */

AGENT_ENV_EXAMPLE RCDATA "deploy/agent.env.example"
